article.description: Randy Culpepper scored 28 points to lead UTEP to an 82-71 win against Texas Tech on Saturday night.
article.headline: Texas Tech defeated by Randy Culpepper-led UTEP
article.linkText: Texas Tech defeated by Culpepper-led UTEP
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- Randy Culpepper scored 28 points to lead UTEP to an 82-71 win against Texas Tech on Saturday night. Culpepper was 9 of 19 shooting with three 3-pointers for the Miners (8-2). Mike Singletary scored 17 points to lead four players in double figures for the Red Raiders (5-6). Julyan Stone had 15 points, 10 rebounds and five assists for UTEP, which beat Texas Tech for the first time since 1997.
